lukdar/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Gold's ascent slows amid volatility</h2> <p>After months of gains and record highs, gold's upward momentum has slowed since early November. Prices have dropped 4% from their October peak to US$2,670/oz<sup>2</sup>. Rising US Treasury</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745737-india-gold-market-update-investment-demand-shines", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 08:01:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745729", "title": "CNH Industrial: Another Guidance Cut, Still A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Harvester combine harvesting wheat on agricultural field on sunny summer day\" data-id=\"1312952454\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312952454/image_1312952454.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36p